Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫心情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是不是
